# Build context is the repo root for every image. Keep it lean and never ship
# host-built artifacts into the image (they're rebuilt inside the container).
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/.next
**/build

.git
.github
.env
.env.*
!.env.*.example

*.log
.DS_Store

# Docs / local tooling that no image needs.
deployment/kubernetes
marketing
specs
*.md
!interfaces/web-app/README.md
